choices.text:
why does this command give error Permission denied (publickey):

ssh -i \“~/UserKey.pem" -C -L 25900:localhost:5900 ec2-34-221-131-108.us-west-2.compute.amazonaws.com
I’d like to use this command, but I don't know what the problem is.  Can you help? 
The error message says that permission has been denied for a key file named “UserKey”, which might be your private key or password (since it starts with an uppercase letter).
